                        </cit>, <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la">
                            <quote> desidia </quote>
                        </cit>, <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la">
                            <quote> inertia </quote>
                        </cit>, <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la">
                            <quote> pigritia </quote>
                        </cit> <ref cRef="Koh." loc="10,18">Koh. 10,18</ref>; <ref cRef="Prov." loc="29,45">Prov. 29,45</ref>; <ref cRef="Sir." loc="22,1">Sir. 22,1</ref>; saepissime in aliis libris, <lbl expand="exempli gratia">ex. gr.</lbl> in Chrys.; <ref cRef="Clem." loc="255">Clem. f. 255</ref>; in juris doctrina <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሀኬት፡</foreign> est <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la">
                            <quote> species culpae </quote>
                        </cit>sc. <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la">
                            <quote> negligentia </quote>
                        </cit>, <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la">
                            <quote> desidia </quote>
                        </cit>, ut: <foreign xml:lang="gez">እመ፡ ዘረከባ፡ እምሕሠማት፡ ኮነ፡ በሀኬተ፡ ዚአሁ፡</foreign> si malum, quod ei (jumento) accidit, <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la">
                            <quote> negligentia </quote>
                        </cit>ejus ortum est F.N. 28; <foreign xml:lang="gez">በ፡ ተሀጕለ፡ ንዋየ፡ አመጋቢ፡ በእደ፡ መጋቢ፡ ዘእንበለ፡ ድልሑት፡ ወኢሀኬት፡</foreign> <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la">
